OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1784733508
OL,3,CTwo riders die in separate British
OL,4,CEventing competitions
OL,6,FTwo female riders have died following
OL,7,Faccidents at separate cross-country
OL,8,Fevents in Cumbria and Oxfordshire.
OL,10,FSophie Fouracre, 34, was fatally
OL,11,Finjured while riding Rhubarbsfox
OL,12,FBrittania in a competition at
OL,13,FSwalcliffe Park in Oxfordshire.
OL,15,FHours later, 42-year-old Kerry
OL,16,FDonoghue died while riding Carneyhaugh
OL,17,FRua in another cross-country event at
OL,18,FPenrith in Cumbria.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
