OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1784733508
OL,3,CTwo riders die in separate British
OL,4,CEventing competitions
OL,6,FLast night British Eventing posted on
OL,7,Fsocial media that a "serious incident"
OL,8,Fhad taken place and that the events,
OL,9,Fwhich were due to run across the
OL,10,Fweekend, would be abandoned.
OL,12,FMedical teams at both the venues are
OL,13,Fsaid to have responded immediately and
OL,14,Fprovided emergency treatment.
OL,16,FThe Great North Air Ambulance was also
OL,17,Fdispatched Frenchfield Farm in Penrith.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
