OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1784733508
OL,3,CTwo riders die in separate British
OL,4,CEventing competitions
OL,6,FIn a statement British Eventing said:
OL,7,F"It is with immense sadness that
OL,8,FBritish Eventing confirms the tragic
OL,9,Floss of Sophie Fouracre and Kerry
OL,10,FDonoghue following separate incidents
OL,11,Fon Saturday 18th July 2026."
OL,13,FOrganisers say the veterinary team
OL,14,Ffound the horses to be uninjured.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
