OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1784733508
OL,3,CTwo riders die in separate British
OL,4,CEventing competitions
OL,6,F"In accordance with British Eventing's
OL,7,Fsafety and incident review procedures,
OL,8,Fcomprehensive reviews of both
OL,9,Faccidents will now be undertaken.:
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Great North Air
OL,12,FAmbulance said: "Our critical care
OL,13,Fteam was activated at 3.21pm to an
OL,14,Fincident in Penrith. We had a
OL,15,Fparamedic and doctor on board our
OL,16,Faircraft and they arrived on scene at
OL,17,F3.26pm."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
